                    '<h2>Patient help and resources</h2>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr"><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="1e8a72b4-c54c-432e-b53a-ef6a7969f40e" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/patient-advocates" title="Patient advocates">Need help? Contact a patient advocate</a></h3>\n\n<p dir="ltr">If you need help getting care or resolving an issue with VA, get help from one of our trained patient advocates.</p>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr"><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="00f8a6a5-37a6-478c-b5d0-4eaa87b5bdd1" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/medical-records-office" title="Medical records office">Medical records office</a></h3>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Access your medical records online or request a copy of your records from our Release of Information office.</p>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr"><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="898aa214-4458-4115-a5c0-fd83302e3efa" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/billing-insurance" title="Billing and insurance">Billing and insurance</a></h3>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Pay your VA Pittsburgh health care bill online, by phone, mail, or in person. You can also raise issues or address billing disputes.</p>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr"><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="d323fc5c-81a7-4388-a3e6-e5a8ff2a3f05" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/pharmacy" title="Pharmacy ">Pharmacy</a></h3>\n\n<p dir="ltr">Find out how to refill your prescriptions, where to pick up new prescription orders, and how to safely dispose of your medicines.</p>\n\n<h2>Phone directory and mailing address</h2>\n\n<p>Find phone numbers for many of the administrative and program offices at VA Pittsburgh health care.</p>\n\n<h3>Mailing address</h3>\n\n<p>VA Pittsburgh Healthcare System<br />\nUniversity Drive C<br />\nPittsburgh, PA 15240-1003</p>\n\n<h3>Main phone numbers</h3>\n\n<p><strong>Local:</strong> <a href="tel: +14128222222">412-822-2222</a><br /><strong>Toll-free:</strong> <a href="tel: +18884827488">866-482-7488</a></p>\n\n<p>To use Telecommunications Device for the Deaf (TDD) services: <strong>dial 711</strong>.</p>',
