                          '<p>The following materials are needed at the H.J. Heinz III campus: </p>\n\n<h4>Personal care</h4>\n\n<ul><li>Battery-operated toothbrushes</li>\n\t<li>Alcohol-free mouthwash</li>\n\t<li>Hairbrushes and combs</li>\n\t<li>Denture cream</li>\n\t<li>Shaving cream</li>\n\t<li>3 and 1 body wash</li>\n\t<li>Shampoo and conditioner</li>\n\t<li>Gloves</li>\n\t<li>Disinfectant wipes</li>\n\t<li>Hand sanitizer</li>\n</ul><h4>Assorted items</h4>\n\n<ul><li>Reading glasses (1.25 and higher)</li>\n\t<li>Wheelchair cup holders</li>\n\t<li>Gift cards</li>\n</ul>',
