                    '<h2><strong>Local transportation options</strong></h2>\n\n<p>Many medical centers and clinics in VAPHS are also served by other local transportation services. To find those, review the transportation services information for <a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="16b03771-b41f-411e-b637-2645083c6bd7" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/locations" title="Locations">the facility you want to visit</a>.</p>',
