                      processed:
                        '<p>Yes, we provide all available images on DVD.</p>\n\n<p>If you have a <a href="https://www.myhealth.va.gov/mhv-portal-web/web/myhealthevet/home">My HealtheVet Premium account</a>, you can also view or download many kinds of radiology images online. A Premium account is one where you’ve gone through extra identity authentication. </p>',
