                      "<h2>Mental health care appointments</h2>\n\n<p>If you're struggling with stress, anxiety, depression, anger, or other issues, we can help. We offer mental health (also called behavioral health) counseling, psychiatric care, and treatment for problems with alcohol and other substances.</p>",
