                                  '<p dir="ltr">Please call the clinic where your appointment is scheduled, so we can give the appointment time to another Veteran.</p>\n\n<ul dir="ltr"><li><strong>For appointments at University Drive or H.J. Heinz:</strong> 866-482-7488, select 2</li>\n\t<li><strong>For mental health (behavioral health) appointments: </strong>412-360-660</li>\n\t<li><strong>For appointments at any of our outpatient clinic: </strong>Call the clinic where you scheduled the appointment. </li>\n</ul><p dir="ltr">If you miss your appointment without letting the clinic know ahead of time, we\'ll consider you a "no show" and you\'ll need to reschedule your appointment.</p>\n\n<p dir="ltr">You can also <a href="https://www.va.gov/health-care/schedule-view-va-appointments/">reschedule or cancel some appointments online</a>.</p>',
