                      "<h2>Get your records online</h2>\n\n<p>Access your VA medical records online with VA Blue Button. Sign in to view, organize, and share your VA medical records and other personal health information. We don't charge any fees to send copies directly to health care providers.</p>\n\n<h3>VA Blue Button</h3>",
