                            '<p>If you\'d like to make a donation to VAPHS, please send a check (payable to "VA Pittsburgh Healthcare System") to the following address:</p>\n\n<p class="va-address-block">VA Pittsburgh Healthcare System<br />\nVoluntary Service (118V-A)<br />\n1010 Delafield Road<br />\nPittsburgh, PA 15215</p>',
