                      '<h2>Cardiology</h2>\n\n<p>VA Pittsburgh\'s staff cardiologists lead national efforts at VA to develop new treatment techniques and are experts at minimally invasive cardiac procedures. VAPHS is also home to a state-of-the-art cardiac catheterization laboratory.</p>\n\n<p><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="016896fb-cf41-4732-83b0-5d14a4607913" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/programs/cardiology" title="Cardiology">Learn more about our cardiology program</a></p>\n\n<h2>GRECC</h2>\n\n<p>The Geriatric Research, Education, and Clinical Centers (GRECCs) are VA centers of excellence focused on aging and promoting top-quality care for older Veterans. The Pittsburgh GRECC has been serving older Veterans in Pennsylvania, Delaware, and parts of West Virginia since 1999.</p>\n\n<p><a data-entity-substitution="canonical" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-uuid="e10eb6bd-f62d-4791-b4b6-558a256274d8" href="/pittsburgh-health-care/research/geriatric-research-education-and-clinical-center-grecc" title="Geriatric Research Education and Clinical Center (GRECC)">Learn more about our GRECC program</a></p>',
