                      '<h2>Contact us</h2>\n\n<p>If you have questions about the PIRATE program, please contact Mary Sullivan, the program Intake Coordinator and Caseworker.</p>\n\n<p class="va-address-block" dir="ltr"><strong>Phone: </strong><a href="tel: +14123606472">412-360-6472</a><br /><strong>Email: </strong><a href="mailto:mary.sullivan@va.gov">mary.sullivan@va.gov</a><br /><strong>Mail:</strong><br />\nVA Pittsburgh Healthcare System<br />\nPIRATE, ATTN Mary Sullivan<br />\nUniversity Drive, 112 SP-U<br />\nPittsburgh, PA  15240</p>',
